query:
INSERT INTO organizations (id, name, slug)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
        ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
        SET name = EXCLUDED.name,
            slug = EXCLUDED.slug,
            updated_at = NOW()
        RETURNING
            id          AS "id!",
            name        AS "name!",
            slug        AS "slug!",
            created_at  AS "created_at!",
            updated_at  AS "updated_at!"
